These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, strawberry, raspberry, grapes
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, cooking, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, satire, time-travel, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, blues, rock
4 different pets are kept: bird, rat, hedgehog, hamster
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the fan of country is the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is the person eating lettuce##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching satire movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | strawberry    | raspberry      | lettuce  | grapes     |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | cooking   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire       | drama | time-travel     | action    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | metal         | country  | blues    |
| Pet           | hedgehog      | hamster       | bird | rat |

