.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, lemonade, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, crime, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, salsa, punk
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, chinchilla, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rugby, weightlifting, climbing
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the owner of the horse is the fan of punk##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is the fan of salsa##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | sprite      | milk     | lemonade    | tea |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | superhero   | crime   | thriller           |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | punk     | salsa    | hip-hop         |
| Pet           | rabbit         | horse | chinchilla     | guinea-pig        |
| Sport         | snowboarding     | climbing  | rugby | weightlifting       |

