.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, radish, zucchini, eggplant
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indonesian, japanese, russian
4 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, dog, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, rowing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person eating zucchini is the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the japanese is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the russian is the owner of the horse##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | grapefruit    | eggplant      | zucchini  | radish   |
| Nationality   | russian     | japanese      | indonesian | colombian      |
| Pet           | horse       | turtle         | goldfish  | dog         |
| Sport         | climbing | sailing | rowing  | volleyball |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | train         | scooter   | taxi        |

