.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: papaya, grapes, blueberry, broccoli
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, mexican, dutch, argentine
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hedgehog, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, motorbike
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the argentine is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the mexican is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk   | iced-tea   | water      | hot-chocolate     |
| Food          | blueberry     | papaya   | broccoli | grapes |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch | polish   | argentine       |
| Pet           | frog       | bird      | fish     | hedgehog |
| Transport     | boat    | ship     | motorbike     | scooter     |

