10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the security-guard is on the far left##1
13. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the dutch is on the right of the thai##1

