 3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 5. the police-officer is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person drinking water is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the van##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the scientist##1
