 7. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the electrician##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | 7up     | lemonade  | almond-milk       | sprite      |
| Hobby       | woodworking    | filmmaking        | magic-tricks  | video-games      |
| Job         | electrician  | doctor | videographer | police-officer |
| Pet         | ferret | lizard          | hedgehog         | goat      |
| Transport   | motorbike     | snowmobile     | scooter       | roller          |

