.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, cola, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, reading, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, zombie, animation
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, nigerian, spanish, polish
4 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, hamster, turtle
 1. the spanish is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the polish is on the left of the russian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the russian is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the owner of the horse is the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | cola      | tea      | fanta    |
| Hobby         | gardening | reading | traveling | drawing  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | drama     | animation      | horror |
| Nationality   | spanish  | polish     | russian    | nigerian  |
| Pet           | horse  | turtle       | ferret          | hamster      |

