.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, nectarine, radish, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, puzzles, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, epic, animation
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, handball, climbing, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bike, boat, van
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating radish##1
11. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
