.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, artichoke, carrot
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, collecting, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, coach, architect, journalist
4 different pets are kept: pony, mouse, rabbit, chinchilla
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, skateboard, quad-bike
 1. the journalist is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the coach##1
 8. the designer is the person driving the car##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person eating carrot is the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | corn    | carrot        | cabbage        | artichoke      |
| Hobby       | collecting       | puzzles       | singing      | board-games |
| Job         | coach | journalist | architect | designer      |
| Pet         | pony          | chinchilla         | mouse           | rabbit    |
| Transport   | skateboard         | taxi       | quad-bike     | car   |

 